    A1 --> B_gate
    A2 -->|"--ai flag absent
skip parsing"| CR_gate

    B_gate -- Yes --> B_gemini --> CR_gate
    B_gate -- No  --> B_kw    --> CR_gate

    CR_gate -- Yes --> CR_gemini --> CR_out
    CR_gate -- No  --> CR_rule  --> CR_out

    CR_out -->|"suggest_alternative:
